# SpaceCadet
# http://stevelosh.com/blog/2012/10/a-modern-space-cadet/#better-shifting

# Control Esc - Left Control sends Esc when tapped alone; Behaves normal in key
# combos. (Happy Vim-ing)
# Better Shifting - Left & Right Shifts send Left & Right Parentheses
xcape -e 'Control_L=Escape;Shift_L=Shift_L|9;Shift_R=Shift_R|0' -t 300
